  <owl:Ontology rdf:about="">
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">1. Changelog::
ConceptPartyAndEntertaiment --&gt; ConceptPartyAndEntertainment
offersAdditionalPartyAndEntertaimentService  --&gt; offersAdditionalPartyAndEntertainmentService
PartyAndEntertayment --&gt; PartyAndEntertainment
MountainShelter --&gt; MountainHut 
VineyardShelter --&gt; VineyardHut
2. Spelling mistakes</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">1. Modificaciones:
ConceptPartyAndEntertaiment --&gt; ConceptPartyAndEntertainment
offersAdditionalPartyAndEntertaimentService  --&gt; offersAdditionalPartyAndEntertainmentService
PartyAndEntertayment --&gt; PartyAndEntertainment
MountainShelter --&gt; MountainHut 
VineyardShelter --&gt; VineyardHut
2. Corrección de errores ortográficos</rdfs:comment>
